00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Aye.

398
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Very well.

399
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
You'll get an additional 40 gee in three days.

400
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Feel free to ask me if you need more.

401
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Anytime.

